# TrustMaven Project Summary

## Goal
Complete all remaining features across Phases 5-9 (Jumpstart Preview, STRM Viewer, Evidence Monitoring, Policy Workflow, Analytics), close all market gaps vs Vanta/Drata, Hyperproof, ServiceNow, Archer, and LogicGate, then expand connectors to 18 total, add AI Co-pilot, OSCAL import pipeline, and connector marketplace — delivering a production-grade open-source GRC platform.

## Constraints & Preferences
- 23+ total pages must be fully connected to backend APIs with proper cross-page navigation
- Every page should present all relevant data from its associated module(s)
- Dashboard must aggregate data from all modules (risks, controls, frameworks, evidence, vendors, policies, audits, integrations, entities)
- Frontend pages should link to related features where applicable (e.g., Risk → FAIR → Entity, Control → Evidence → Frameworks)
- No new database models unless required — all existing 43 models must be leveraged

